<div id="review_2655143491" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2655143491" />
    <a title="Claudia " class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/46554514-claudia"><img alt="Claudia " src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1572204658p2/46554514.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2655143491?book_show_action=true">Dec 01, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Claudia " class="user" itemprop="url" name="Claudia " href="/user/show/46554514-claudia">Claudia </a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2655143491" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4708596938709177226">My first Virginia Woolf novel! I really enjoyed this story built around romantic relationships and friendships between four young people in early 20th century London. It is quite a long book with a slow-paced plot and a lot of inner monologue, but that suits me just fine.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review2655143491">
  <td colspan="2">
